Gigan's stasis pod heads down to the planet's suface. He lands in what is now called Argentina. His DNA scanners scan the fossil DNA of a dinosaur called Giganotosaurus. 
With his new beast mode, Gigan starts up his stasis pod again and travels back up into space where he saw the Maximal/Autobot ship, The ARK.
